725825f-a.title: Queens: 120th Street - 85th Avenue
725825f-a.text:
120th Street, at the S. E. corner of 85th Avenue. In 1918
the house was known as the Democratic Club of Richmond Hill and
in 1891 it was ewned by E. M. Bronson.
P. L. Sperr  April 23, 1936
